#: ../../../../CHANGES.md:30
msgid ""
"Stop splitting between a variable and its comparator (`not in`, `==`, "
"`is`, ...) when the right-hand side is a bracketed expression. Black now "
"lets the bracket explode instead. This fixes the awkward break that was "
"showing up in comprehension `if` clauses ([#4514](https://github.com/psf/"
"black/pull/4514)) as well as the same shape inside `if`, `elif`, `assert`, "
"and parenthesized expressions ([#5135](https://github.com/psf/black/"
"pull/5135))"
msgstr ""

