#: ../../../../CHANGES.md:1009
msgid ""
"Upgrade mypyc from 0.991 to 1.3 ([#3697](https://github.com/psf/black/"
"pull/3697))"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGES.md:1010
msgid ""
"Remove patching of Click that mitigated errors on Python 3.6 with `LANG=C` "
"([#3768](https://github.com/psf/black/pull/3768))"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGES.md:1014
msgid ""
"Add support for the new PEP 695 syntax in Python 3.12 ([#3703](https://"
"github.com/psf/black/pull/3703))"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGES.md:1018
msgid ""
"Speed up _Black_ significantly when the cache is full ([#3751](https://"
"github.com/psf/black/pull/3751))"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGES.md:1019
msgid ""
"Avoid importing `IPython` in a case where we wouldn't need it ([#3748]"
"(https://github.com/psf/black/pull/3748))"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGES.md:1023
msgid ""
"Use aware UTC datetimes internally, avoids deprecation warning on Python "
